item.title: CVE-2019-0343|2024-08-04T17:44:16.564Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20commerce%20cloud%20%28mediaconversion%20extension%29
item.description: SAP Commerce Cloud (Mediaconversion Extension), versions 6.4, 6.5, 6.6, 6.7, 1808, 1811, 1905, allows an authenticated Backoffice/HMC user to inject code that can be executed by the application, leading to Code Injection. An attacker could thereby control the behavior of the application.
